<strong>Worker</strong> page."},{"content":"We recommend that you verify that the seniority date field always has a value.","pos":[7522,7600]},{"content":"If you use the seniority date to determine the months of service, and the <bpt id=\"p1\">&lt;strong&gt;</bpt>Seniority date<ept id=\"p1\">&lt;/strong&gt;</ept> field on the <bpt id=\"p2\">&lt;strong&gt;</bpt>Worker<ept id=\"p2\">&lt;/strong&gt;</ept> page is blank, the worker can use hours from the benefit accrual plan, but no hours can accrue in the plan.","pos":[7601,7851],"source":" If you use the seniority date to determine the months of service, and the <strong>Seniority date</strong> field on the <strong>Worker</strong> page is blank, the worker can use hours from the benefit accrual plan, but no hours can accrue in the plan."},{"content":"<bpt id=\"p1\">&lt;strong&gt;</bpt>Annual plan start date<ept id=\"p1\">&lt;/strong&gt;</ept>","pos":[7861,7900],"source":"<strong>Annual plan start date</strong>"},{"content":"<bpt id=\"p1\">&lt;strong&gt;</bpt>Custom date<ept id=\"p1\">&lt;/strong&gt;</ept> – A date that is specified for this plan.","pos":[7910,7980],"source":"<strong>Custom date</strong> – A date that is specified for this plan."},{"content":"<bpt id=\"p1\">\n&lt;strong&gt;</bpt>Note:<ept id=\"p1\">&lt;/strong&gt;</ept> This field is available only when the accrual rate basis is <bpt id=\"p2\">&lt;strong&gt;</bpt>Fixed amount by date<ept id=\"p2\">&lt;/strong&gt;</ept>.","pos":[7991,8113],"source":"\n<strong>Note:</strong> This field is available only when the accrual rate basis is <strong>Fixed amount by date</strong>."},{"content":"Custom accrual date","pos":[8146,8165]},{"content":"The month and date each year when the number of hours in the <bpt id=\"p1\">&lt;strong&gt;</bpt>Amount or rate<ept id=\"p1\">&lt;/strong&gt;</ept> field is added to the plan balance.","pos":[8175,8303],"source":"The month and date each year when the number of hours in the <strong>Amount or rate</strong> field is added to the plan balance."},{"content":"<bpt id=\"p1\">&lt;strong&gt;</bpt>Note:<ept id=\"p1\">&lt;/strong&gt;</ept> This field is available only when the accrual rate basis is <bpt id=\"p2\">&lt;strong&gt;</bpt>Fixed amount by date<ept id=\"p2\">&lt;/strong&gt;</ept> and the accrual date is <bpt id=\"p3\">&lt;strong&gt;</bpt>Custom date<ept id=\"p3\">&lt;/strong&gt;</ept>.","pos":[8304,8478],"source":"<strong>Note:</strong> This field is available only when the accrual rate basis is <strong>Fixed amount by date</strong> and the accrual date is <strong>Custom date</strong>."},{"content":"The following information can be entered on the <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Plan rules<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> FastTab.","pos":[8509,8580],"source":"The following information can be entered on the **Plan rules** FastTab."},{"content":"Each line that you add to a benefit accrual plan provides the rules for accruing time and using plan benefits for workers who have the specified number of months of service.","pos":[8581,8754]},{"content":"Field","pos":[8758,8763]},{"content":"Description","pos":[8782,8793]},{"content":"Months of service","pos":[11452,11469]},{"content":"The minimum number of months of service for the selected rule.","pos":[11476,11538]},{"content":"The number of months of service is based on the employment start date, the seniority date, or a date that is specified for the worker on the <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Benefit accruals<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> page.","pos":[11539,11706],"source":" The number of months of service is based on the employment start date, the seniority date, or a date that is specified for the worker on the **Benefit accruals** page."},{"content":"<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Note:<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> The employment start date is on the <bpt id=\"p2\">**</bpt>Employment history<ept id=\"p2\">**</ept> page, and the seniority date is on the <bpt id=\"p3\">**</bpt>Worker<ept id=\"p3\">**</ept> page.","pos":[11707,11831],"source":"**Note:** The employment start date is on 